A paragraph with \emph{emphasis}, \textbf{strong emphasis}, and
\texttt{inline\ literal} text.

A second paragraph that spans two source lines joined by a soft break.

Escapes keep a literal *asterisk* intact, and an inline literal can
attach to a word like with\texttt{code} mid-sentence.
